DTEND:20190204T145500
DESCRIPTION;ALTREP="https://cfgmgmtcamp.eu/schedule/monday/opscontainer/":Ops hates containers! Why?
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:@"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><HTML><BODY><p>&ldquo;Docker, Docker, Docker, Docker, &hellip;&rdquo;, developers really love Docker.<br />
