ORGANIZER:Jorie Tappa
CATEGORIES:talk
DTSTAMP:20181231T000000Z
TZID:Europe-Brussels
DTSTART:20190204T150000
DTEND:20190204T155500
DESCRIPTION;ALTREP="https://cfgmgmtcamp.eu/schedule/monday/puppettype/":Puppet's Type & Provider Module Extraction Saga
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:@"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><HTML><BODY><p>In Puppet 6, we removed several core types and providers into modules, and published most of those onto the Puppet Forge.<br />
