METHOD:PUBLISH
UID:foremanrel@cfgmgmtcamp.eu
SUMMARY:The Foreman Release Process and Roadmap
ORGANIZER:Tomer Brisker
CATEGORIES:talk
DTSTAMP:20181229T000000Z
TZID:Europe-Brussels
DTSTART:20190204T140000
DTEND:20190204T145500
DESCRIPTION;ALTREP="https://cfgmgmtcamp.eu/schedule/monday/foremanrel/":The Foreman Release Process and Roadmap
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:@"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><HTML><BODY><p>The first part of the talk will be a short description of the release process of Foreman,
as well as some changes that have been made to it over the past year to ensure higher quality releases.<br />
The second part will be an open discussion of the roadmap for the upcoming releases.<br />
This is your chance to influence the future direction of the Foreman project - come and say your opinions!</p>
</BODY></HTML>";
