TZID:Europe-Brussels
DTSTART:20190204T150000
DTEND:20190204T155500
DESCRIPTION;ALTREP="https://cfgmgmtcamp.eu/schedule/monday/ruddernext/":What happened in Rudder in 2018 and what's next?
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:@"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ""-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN""><HTML><BODY><p>Let&rsquo;s take a look at Rudder&rsquo;s new features from 2018,
both in terms of the features of versions 4.3 and 5.0
